  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078330/extras/1d767073bc0c4d7185228d9ca27134cb.avif?t=1749283260\" width=576 height=324 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Liz and her mentor Aisha, are talented witches. But despite their talent, a thief manages to steal a powerful tome called the “Grimoire of Darkness” from them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chasing after the man, they end up near the town of Bramach. Aisha senses danger emanating from the area and orders Liz to stay behind.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, unwilling to heed her mentor’s words, Liz heads into the town to continue her pursuit of the thief.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic RPG Experience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore an immersive fantasy world</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn-based Combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crafting</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078330/extras/1d767073bc0c4d7185228d9ca27134cb.avif?t=1749283260\" width=576 height=324 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Liz and her mentor Aisha, are talented witches. But despite their talent, a thief manages to steal a powerful tome called the “Grimoire of Darkness” from them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chasing after the man, they end up near the town of Bramach. Aisha senses danger emanating from the area and orders Liz to stay behind.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, unwilling to heed her mentor’s words, Liz heads into the town to continue her pursuit of the thief.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic RPG Experience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore an immersive fantasy world</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn-based Combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crafting</p></li></ul>",
